snippet.title: A HAND WITH MANY FINGERS - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
AVAILABLE ON 9 JUNE

WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1229030/A_Hand_With_Many_Fingers/
FOLLOW ON ITCH.IO: https://colestia.itch.io/a-hand-with-many-fingers

A Hand With Many Fingers is a first-person investigative thriller. While searching a dusty CIA archive you uncover a real Cold War conspiracy. Every document you find has new leads to research. But the archive might not be as empty as you think…
